'''黃偉軒'''（{{bd|1991年|11月30日||}}）是台灣[[区块链|區塊鏈]]與[[加密貨幣|加密貨幣]]產業企業家，目前為 Steaker 數位資產管理平台創辦人暨執行長、去中心化跨鏈聚合器 XY Finance 創辦人。

== 生平 ==
2014 年就讀台大資工系期間購入[[比特幣|比特幣]]，發掘區塊鏈與加密貨幣產業的潛力，開始進行[[以太幣|以太幣]][[挖礦|挖礦]]<ref>{{cite news |url = https://tw.news.yahoo.com/video/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A32-0%E8%88%88%E8%B5%B7-%E8%B3%87%E5%B7%A5%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB%E6%94%B9%E6%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%A3-143600240.html |title = 比特幣2.0興起! 資工碩士改挖以太幣 |publisher = Yahoo!新聞 |date = 2017-05-25 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-09-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210913175107/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/video/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A32-0%E8%88%88%E8%B5%B7-%E8%B3%87%E5%B7%A5%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB%E6%94%B9%E6%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%A3-143600240.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>以及相關研究；2015 年就讀台大資訊工程暨網路媒體研究所，主要進行[[分散式運算|分散式運算]]、[[共識機制|共識機制]]的開發研究<ref>{{Cite thesis |degree= 臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所學位|title= 區塊鏈共識演算法之比較與分析|url= https://www.airitilibrary.com/Publication/alDetailedMesh?docid=U0001-0108201712385500|author= 黃偉軒|year= 2017/01/01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite thesis|degree= 臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所學位|title= 區塊鏈共識演算法之比較與分析|url= https://ndltd.ncl.edu.tw/cgi-bin/gs32/gsweb.cgi/login?o=dnclcdr&s=id=%22105NTU05641039%22.&searchmode=basic|author= 黃偉軒|year= 2017/01/01|access-date= 2020-12-06|archive-date= 2021-09-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210913202126/https://ndltd.ncl.edu.tw/cgi-bin/gs32/gsweb.cgi/login?o=dnclcdr&s=id=%22105NTU05641039%22.&searchmode=basic|dead-url= no}}</ref>，以及[[密码货币钱包|加密貨幣錢包]]的開發，並舉辦台大黑客松<ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5070466
 |title = 黑客松精神　讓創新種子發光 |publisher = 天下雜誌 |date =2015-09-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.appacus.org.tw/files/file_pool/2/0I170335189916081725/%E5%95%86%E5%91%A8.compressed.pdf |title = 半年飆 46 被，超貨幣時代來了 |publisher = 商業週刊 |date = 2017/06 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-10-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211020081156/http://www.appacus.org.tw/files/file_pool/2/0I170335189916081725/%E5%95%86%E5%91%A8.compressed.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>，亦曾參與[[中華民國中央銀行|中華民國中央銀行]]票據交換所清算業務的區塊鏈 PoC（Proof-of-Concept）<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.panewslab.com/zh/articledetails/1605014937269672.html |title = 获V神点赞，帮黄立成操刀区块链项目，Wilson Huang 创办Steaker让交易更容易 |publisher = PANewsLab |date = 2020-11-10 |accessdate = 2020-12-06 |archive-date = 2021-11-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211123114938/https://www.panewslab.com/zh/articledetails/1605014937269672.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2017 年碩士畢業後，黃偉軒曾擔任[[Yahoo奇摩|Yahoo奇摩]]軟體工程師；後續加入秘銀科技，並於 2018 年擔任副總裁<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.credit.com.tw/NewCreditOnline/Epaper/InterviewContent.aspx?sn=41&unit=454 |title = 新興產業「秘銀」與新星副總 |publisher = 中華徵信所 |date = 2019-01-15 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-10-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211020225157/http://www.credit.com.tw/NewCreditOnline/Epaper/InterviewContent.aspx?sn=41&unit=454 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。曾參與[[以太坊|以太坊]]第二層功能的擴展與開發，且獲得 ETH Grant<ref>{{cite web|url= https://blog.ethereum.org/2018/03/07/announcing-beneficiaries-ethereum-foundation-grants/|title= Announcing Beneficiaries of the Ethereum Foundation Grant|date= 2018-03-07|website= Ethereum Blog|access-date= 2020-12-08|archive-date= 2021-03-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210321235609/https://blog.ethereum.org/2018/03/07/announcing-beneficiaries-ethereum-foundation-grants/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

2019 年創辦 Steaker<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.gvm.com.tw/article/56193 |title = 不甘只做資訊工程師 從興趣中邂逅創業契機 |publisher = 遠見 |date = 2019-02-25 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-01-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115171435/https://www.gvm.com.tw/article/56193 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並在兩年之內帶領團隊創造相當於 5,500 萬美元的{{tsl|en|Assets under management|資產管理規模|資產管理規模}}<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.dealstreetasia.com/stories/quintype-steaker-216146/ |title = Asia Digest: India's Quintype raises $3.4m Series A; Taiwan's Steaker bags $1m |publisher = 遠見 |date = 2020-11-10 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2020-12-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201204145926/https://www.dealstreetasia.com/stories/quintype-steaker-216146/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並於 2020 年 10 月入選 [[AppWorks|AppWorks]] 第 20 期新創加速器<ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.inside.com.tw/article/21234-AppWorks-Demo-Day-2020|title = AppWorks Demo Day 2020 登場，合體估值突破 3203 億台幣|publisher = INSIDE 硬塞的網路趨勢觀察|date = 2020-10-15|accessdate = 2020-12-04|archive-date = 2021-01-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120201331/https://www.inside.com.tw/article/21234-AppWorks-Demo-Day-2020|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2021 年，榮獲 Tatler Taiwan 雜誌評選為 Generation T 亞洲未來的新銳先鋒。<ref>{{cite news|url = https://www.tatlerasia.com/the-scene/people-parties/2021%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8gent-%E5%BD%A2%E5%A1%91%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%8430%E4%BD%8D%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3gent%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%B3%E5%85%88%E5%B3%B0|title = 2021年最新入選Gen.T！ 形塑亞洲未來的30位台灣Gen.T新銳先峰|publisher = Tatler Asia|date = 2021-09-16|accessdate = 2021-10-25|archive-date = 2021-10-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211027002911/https://www.tatlerasia.com/the-scene/people-parties/2021%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8gent-%E5%BD%A2%E5%A1%91%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%8430%E4%BD%8D%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3gent%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%B3%E5%85%88%E5%B3%B0|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 评价 ==
台灣區塊鏈媒體動區動趨將其列為「區塊鏈產業最有影響力的意見領袖」之一<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.blocktempo.com/taiwan-kol-2020-prdictions/ |title = 來自台灣區塊鏈產業的禮物: 18 位最有影響力的從業者和 KOL 的「2020 年預測」 |publisher = BlockTempo 動區動趨 |date = 2020-01-02 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-01-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126181411/https://www.blocktempo.com/taiwan-kol-2020-prdictions/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並受邀擔任 2020 台北金融博覽會財經論壇的講者<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.blocktempo.com/crypto-and-blockchain-area-in-2020-taipei-finexpo/ |title = 動區特派員｜2020 金融博覽會登場，首屆「加密金融主題館」驚艷全場，三大亮點報給你聽！ |publisher = BlockTempo 動區動趨 |date = 2020-11-28 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-03-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210302173319/https://www.blocktempo.com/crypto-and-blockchain-area-in-2020-taipei-finexpo/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，與前金管會主委{{tsl|en|Wang Li-ling|王儷玲|王儷玲}}、MaiCoin 集團執行長暨共同創辦人劉世偉同台，發表對於加密金融產業的趨勢洞察。

==言论==
黃偉軒认为，比特幣為加密金融帶來的第一個突破是實現「價值轉移」，并对[[以太坊|以太坊]]上去中心化金融領域（DeFi）大加赞赏<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.blocktempo.com/2020-taipei-finexpo-introduce-u-blockchain-and-crypto-finance |title = 金融博覽會｜前金管會主委：Libra 推動了 CBDC；穩定幣將引領加密金融發展 |publisher = BlockTempo 動區動趨 |date = 2020-11-28 |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-02-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227132528/https://www.blocktempo.com/2020-taipei-finexpo-introduce-u-blockchain-and-crypto-finance/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

